{"tid":361971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啟晴邨大火79歲獨居老翁亡 200住客疏散瞓街","createTime":"2017-08-16T14:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T08:00:03.000Z","uid":82640,"like":23,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1275cc40f9696d8fb19702c819ea15101bf1d21c","tid":361971,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:12:13.000Z","msg":"晚上7時許，九龍灣<span style=\"color: red;\">啟晴邨</span>悅晴樓27樓一單位突然失火，大量濃煙由窗口冒出，火光熊熊，街坊報警。消防員到場出動兩隊煙帽隊及開動兩條喉射水灌救，約30分鐘將火救熄。<br />\n<br />\n消防員入屋赫見一名<span style=\"color: red;\">老翁（79歲）</span>倒臥昏迷，將他救出，由救護員送院，經搶救後不治。警方經初步調查後，相信死者獨居上址，正封鎖現場調查起火原因。事件中，<span style=\"color: red;\">約200名住客須疏散樓下，仍有居民未獲準返回單位</span>。現場消息稱，死者是一名獨居老翁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170816/photo/bkn-20170816204835982-0816_00822_001_04b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170816%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170816204835982-0816_00822_001_04b.jpg&h=0d0f9e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170816/photo/bkn-20170816204835982-0816_00822_001_03b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170816%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170816204835982-0816_00822_001_03b.jpg&h=696ef3b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db38df3ec3432cb99f492d4b6812b6e78819702e","tid":361971,"uid":29702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:15:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3267edaed0aecdfb8cd7af714873921f822862f4","tid":361971,"uid":189,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"張相全部妹吓妹吓"},{"pid":"8e82a5d678f42238b1ffec07495bf0e55a61cf18","tid":361971,"uid":62314,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"一個短褲屋邨妹都冇，啟睛邨點搞架"},{"pid":"3dd357e386723a8f040aa196071b2ddc121e2d84","tid":361971,"uid":26451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T14:20:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除